overview:
RS Exports was established in 1993 at Chennai in Tamil Nadu, India. The company has been working successfully under the wise guidance of Mr. W.V. Raajendra Prasad, CEO of the company, having more than 3 decades of business experience.

Our Quality: We are one of the fastest growing firms and have the distinction of supplying Quality, Quantity and Flawless Services to all our customers.

Vendor Base: Owing to the long lasting relationship with our vendors, our company has been able to efficiently address the diverse demands and requirements of our valued clients.

Our Team: We have a perfect team of professionals who are consistently engaged to complete their allotted work flawlessly and without any delay.

Why Us: Our company has been working successfully in the field of offering Non Coking Coal, Industrial Scrap, Iron Ore and products since so many years.

Our Products: Coking Coal U.S. Coking Coal Australian Coking Coal Non Coking Coal Industrial Scrap. Iron Ore
